Package: ogrdbstats
Type: Package
Title: Standardised reporting of genotype statistics
Version: 0.3.1
Author: William Lees
Maintainer: William Lees <william@lees.org.uk>
Description: Multiple tools are now available for inferring the personalised Ig genotype from an immune repertoire. 
    Ogrdbstats can read the output from a number of these tools, converting to a standard format and 
    supplementing with additional rich data such as usage and characterisation of 'novel' alleles. Reports 
    and charts can be created for review and upload to ORGDB (https://ogrdb.airr-community.org).
License: CC BY-SA 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
